from.S: rundown.access_rules r left join broadcast.access_rules b on r._id = b._id and b.date_processed >= getdate()-1

select.S: r._id, case when b._id is not null then True else False end, r.date_processed as start_date, dense_rank() over (order by r._id) as combo_id,  row_number() over (partition by r._id order by r.date_processed) as row_num, getdate() as date_processed
